title: The.Wolf.Among.Us.Episode.4.In.Sheeps.Clothing.DLC.XBOX360.rar
description:
The Wolf Among Us takes place prior to the comics and lets players take on the role of Bigby Wolf (The Big Bad Wolf), who has been exiled to New York City. The game follows Wolf as he tries to keep fairy tale characters including Mr. Toad and the Three Little Pigs undetected in our world.
